Jenifer Abaho Muheesi bụ onye nnọchi anya ụmụ nwanyị Ugandan nke Kazo District n'okpuru National Resistance Movement (NRM) na nke iri na otu nke Uganda
Jenifer nọdụrụ asambodo agụmakwụkwọ ya na Uganda site na ụlọ akwụkwọ sekọndrị ụmụ nwanyị nke Kibura

Onye bụbu Minista na-ahụ maka nlekota akụ na ụba, Molly Kamukama tinyere akwụkwọ mkpesa na-egbochi nhọpụta Jennifer Muheesi dị ka onye na-ebu ọkọlọtọ NRM maka Kazo District Woman Member of Parliament. Ụlọikpe Kasị Elu dị na Mbarara jụrụ nke ahụ na-azọrọ na ntuli aka nke National Resistance Movement mebiri na mmebi iwu mgbe e meriri Molly
